### Santé
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Connexion (élève de démo)
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+22900000000",
  "password": "lasylab"
}

### Inscription
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "firstName": "Eleve",
  "phone": "+22911111111",
  "password": "secret123",
  "birthYear": 2009,
  "school": "Mon école",
  "role": "student",
  "consent": true
}

### Profil courant (remplacer <TOKEN> par accessToken de la connexion)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Mise à jour du profil (onboarding classe/objectif)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classe": "1ère",
  "objectif": "Réussir mon examen"
}

### Matières
GET http://localhost:3000/api/subjects
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Progression
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress/me
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
